# Transparently proxy backend-served static assets (generated illustration PNGs)
# from this Cloudflare Pages origin to the Fly backend, so the relative URLs
# returned by the API (e.g. /static/runs/<id>/scene_0.png) resolve from the
# Pages domain without backend or frontend code changes.
#
# Trailing `200` makes this a server-side rewrite (proxy), not a redirect.
/static/*  https://anime-illustrator-api.fly.dev/static/:splat  200

# SPA fallback for vue-router history mode — deep links like /runs/<id> must
# serve index.html instead of 404'ing. Cloudflare Pages usually does this
# automatically for missing files, but we're explicit so the contract is
# documented in source and host-portable.
/*         /index.html                                          200
